long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Talking Tom Spot Differences is an engaging game where you'll encounter various locations and encounter mischievous toys that have sprung to life, creating dangerous situations. Your mission is to find the differences within the given time frame. This game is both enjoyable and educational, as it helps enhance your observation and concentration skills. With 20 levels to explore, each featuring 7 differences, you'll be challenged to spot them all before time runs out.
